{
  "stem": "3022.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In exchange for saving the lives of those people, the eldest of the prisoners promised to vouch for the camp commandant when the Americans will liberate.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When the SS heard that, they started disappearing into the woods.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we ran into the night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We eventually found ourselves in a barn in the outskirts of a village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we went into this particular barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But before we went, we took with us one SS man, who was really not an SS man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We watched the SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We knew who was mean, who was bad, who was good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was an old Hungarian, ethnic German, who, when the Germans went into Hungary, they put him into the Wehrmacht first.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They put him first into the whatever they would call the land army and then to the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That man, he couldn't even speak German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He never hurt anybody, never harmed anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we took him with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were in the barn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he used to go out and get food for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "On May 1-- it was strange.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "May 1, in the morning, when we woke up, it snowed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was already spring, it was warm already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But May 1, it snowed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The whole landscape was covered in snow, as if nature wanted to cover out the blood-soaken earth, put a mantle of innocence on it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we heard rumblings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when we looked through the barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we saw tanks with five-pointed stars on them and soldiers next to it, marching through the road.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "At first, we thought these were Russians, because to us a five-pointed star would indicate Russians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But when we looked at the soldiers, somebody says, no, no, they're Americans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They're Americans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they went into the village.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
